C. QUICK WINS SUMMARY
   Top 3 changes that would give the biggest performance improvement with least code change.
   Estimate performance gain for each (e.g. "removing iterrows from file X → estimated 3–5× speedup").

OUTPUT: Save as ./analysis/03_pandas_audit.html
Use a findings table with colour-coded severity rows:
